profile_positions.description:
Investigar, analizar y proponer tecnologías de generación eléctrica para el
aprovechamiento de los Residuos Sólidos Municipales (MSW) generados por el
Municipio de Mosquera.

Comparar las tecnologías anteriormente mencionadas, teniendo en cuenta su
potencial de generación eléctrica y viabilidad financiera, con el propósito de
desarrollar un proyecto piloto en el municipio.
profile_positions.title: Junior Research Assistant

company.name: Electrolux Group
company.description:
Electrolux Group is a leading global appliance company that has shaped living for the better for more than 100 years. We reinvent taste, care and wellbeing experiences for millions of people, always striving to be at the forefront of sustainability in society through our solutions and operations. Under our group of leading appliance brands, including Electrolux, AEG and Frigidaire, we sell approximately 60 million household products in more than 120 markets every year. In 2022 Electrolux Group had sales of SEK 135 billion and employed 51,000 people around the world. For more information, go to www.electroluxgroup.com
